title: Fatal Shooting at Sydney’s Bondi on Hanukkah
description:
Several people were killed at a Hanukkah celebration on Sydney’s Bondi Beach after gunmen opened fire, an incident the Australian prime minister called a “targeted attack” on the Jewish community.

 (Source: Bloomberg)
